      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks or stone chips, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or wear, and the original factory scent remains preserved. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive driver aids, functions with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It has never seen rain, let alone snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. Included are both original keys, all owner manuals, and a custom car cover. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
